Class ModifyPartFormController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.ModifyPartFormController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable
    public class ModifyPartFormController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    This class controls the Modify Part Form. Allows the user to modify parts in the inventory.

        public void sendPart​(Part part)

      • saveHandler

        private void saveHandler​(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
                  throws java.io.IOException
        Saves the part to be modified. When pressed, the Save button will get the data entered in the text fields and check them to be sure max is greater than min and inv is between max and min. The part is checked to see if it is InHouse or Outsourced and given the appropriate attribute.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
